
Taurus region hosts 6 karst springs from Türkiye. 

The discharge data are obtained from 2 different sources:

Mehmet Çelik (mehmetcelik@ankara.edu.tr) and
Turkish State Hydraulic Works "https://dsi.gov.tr"

Turkish State Hydraulic Works publish discharge annual reports publicly as PDF files. 
The data curation team downloaded and digitized the discharge data.
Permission for the re-distribution of the data is obtained by Süleyman Selim Çallı (scalli@ankara.edu.tr).

For more information, please see the Metadata table.
